      "chapterTitle": "三",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300020505_5_5716-5932",
          "range": "5716-5932",
          "rangeStart": 5716,
          "rangeEnd": 5932,
          "markText": "我发现我那让每样东西都回归其位、每种事物都遵循其时、每个用词都符合其韵的偏执并不是有序思维的奖赏，与之相反，它是一整套由我发明的假象系统，为的是掩盖我天性中的混乱无序。安分守己并不是我的美德，而是一种对抗粗心大意的反应，我表现得慷慨是为了遮掩我的吝啬，我装作谨慎克己因为我满脑子恶念，我温和是为了不向自己被压抑的怒火屈服，我守时只是为了掩饰他人的时间对我来说多么不重要。总而言之，我发现爱情不是一种精神状态而是黄道十二宫的一个星座。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1724082272,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-19 23:44:32",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5716&rangeEnd=5932",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5716&rangeEnd=5932"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_536-569",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "536-569",
      "markText": "活到九十岁这年，我想找个年少的处女，送自己一个充满疯狂爱欲的夜晚。",
      "totalCount": 1950,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=536&rangeEnd=569",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=536&rangeEnd=569"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_7_2544-2584",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2544-2584",
      "markText": "感谢上帝，我及时遇见了我的中国人。那感觉就像嫁给了一根小拇指，但他是我一个人的。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2544&rangeEnd=2584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2544&rangeEnd=2584"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_4608-4673",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4608-4673",
      "markText": "我从二十岁左右开始做记录，包含名字、年龄、地点以及对情境和风格的简要提示。到五十岁时，我已经分别和五百一十四个女人至少睡过一次了。",
      "totalCount": 832,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4608&rangeEnd=4673",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4608&rangeEnd=4673"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_6_1510-1579",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1510-1579",
      "markText": "她的声音有种平庸的味道，仿佛发出它的并不是她本人而是她携带于体内的另一个人。所有的疑影都在那一刻从我的灵魂中消失了：我还是更喜欢睡着的她。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1510&rangeEnd=1579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1510&rangeEnd=1579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_7_9869-9917",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "9869-9917",
      "markText": "终于，真正的生活开始了，我的心安然无恙，注定会在百岁之后的某日，在幸福的弥留之际死于美好的爱情。",
      "totalCount": 650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9869&rangeEnd=9917",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9869&rangeEnd=9917"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_5_7813-7832",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7813-7832",
      "markText": "性是一个人在不能得到爱时给自己的安慰。",
      "totalCount": 637,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7813&rangeEnd=7832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7813&rangeEnd=7832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_971-999",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "971-999",
      "markText": "世界上最后的“处女”只剩你们这种生在八月的处女座的人了。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=971&rangeEnd=999",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=971&rangeEnd=999"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_4_7807-7857",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7807-7857",
      "markText": "我挂了电话，全身被一种生命中前所未有的解放感充盈，终于，我从自我十三岁起便开始奴役我的束缚中解脱了。",
      "totalCount": 512,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7807&rangeEnd=7857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7807&rangeEnd=7857"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_7929-7974",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7929-7974",
      "markText": "一分钟都不能早到，因为小姑娘要先哄弟弟妹妹吃饭睡觉，还要照顾因风湿病而瘫痪的母亲上床休息。",
      "totalCount": 490,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7929&rangeEnd=7974",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7929&rangeEnd=7974"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_6100-6162",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6100-6162",
      "markText": "等到晚上十一点编辑部关门后，我真正的生活才会开始。每星期我都会在红灯区睡两三晚，床伴的数量之多甚至让我两次荣膺年度客户桂冠。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6100&rangeEnd=6162",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6100&rangeEnd=6162"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_4_4495-4563",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4495-4563",
      "markText": "我们这一代人年轻的时候对生活都太贪婪，以致身体和灵魂都忘记了对未来的期盼，直到现实告诉我们未来和我们曾经的梦想不一样，便又开始怀恋旧日。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4495&rangeEnd=4563",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4495&rangeEnd=4563"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_5_3347-3384",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3347-3384",
      "markText": "如今，我知道那不是幻觉，而是又一个奇迹，一个在九十岁时逢遇人生初恋的奇迹。",
      "totalCount": 464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3347&rangeEnd=3384",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3347&rangeEnd=3384"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_5_2856-2893",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2856-2893",
      "markText": "回答她时我说了实话：一个人的年龄并不是他有多少岁，而是他感觉自己有多少岁。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2856&rangeEnd=2893",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2856&rangeEnd=2893"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_4724-4793",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4724-4793",
      "markText": "我不曾参加多人狂欢，也从未在公共场合与人淫乐，我没有分享过秘密也未曾向人讲述过任何灵与肉的冒险之旅，因为从年轻时起我就明白：凡事皆有报应。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4724&rangeEnd=4793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4724&rangeEnd=4793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_7_3555-3580",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3555-3580",
      "markText": "一股烈火点燃了我的五脏六腑。只可能是做婊子，我说。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3555&rangeEnd=3580",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3555&rangeEnd=3580"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_7_2000-2031",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2000-2031",
      "markText": "事实就是你并没有从内心感觉到老，但所有其他人都从外面看出来了。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2000&rangeEnd=2031",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2000&rangeEnd=2031"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_4_7163-7211",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7163-7211",
      "markText": "我突然想到，年老的一个美妙之处就在于，年轻的女性朋友会放松地挑逗我们，因为她们都觉得我们不行了。",
      "totalCount": 350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7163&rangeEnd=7211",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7163&rangeEnd=7211"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_3_3291-3344",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3291-3344",
      "markText": "事实上，那些最早的变化缓慢到几乎难以洞悉，当一个人内心仍感觉一切如故时，他人却能从其外表察觉到改变的发生。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3291&rangeEnd=3344",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3291&rangeEnd=3344"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_5_7166-7204",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7166-7204",
      "markText": "名气是一位很胖的女士，她不和你睡觉，但当你醒来的时候，她永远都在床边看着你。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7166&rangeEnd=7204",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7166&rangeEnd=7204"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020505_4_6286-6330",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6286-6330",
      "markText": "秘书们把一个蛋糕拿进了大厅，上面插着九十根点燃的蜡烛，它们逼我第一次直面自己年龄的数字。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020505&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6286&rangeEnd=6330",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cdf32c10813ab6e82g0150f4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6286&rangeEnd=6330"
    }
